  <header>
    <h2 class="section-heading half-block screen-reader">Study at Bath</h2>
  </header>
  <div class="section-wrapper">
    <div class="flex-row-reverse flex-column-sm">
      <!-- Image -->
      <div class="half-block hide-for-small-only">
        <img class="stretch" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/52371396945_89370af824_c_d.jpg" alt="Graduates taking selfie" loading="lazy">
      </div>
      <!-- Text bucket -->
      <div class="half-block">
        <div class="text-block flex-column flex-center">
          <h1>A springboard for success</h1>

<p>As the University celebrates being named University of the Year in The Times and The Sunday Times Good University Guide 2023, we delve deeper into what makes Bath such a special place to study.</p>

<p>Find out <a href="https://stories.bath.ac.uk/a-springboard-for-success/">what it takes to be named University of the Year</a>.</p>

<h1>International webinars</h1>

<p>If you live outside the UK, <a href="/events/apply-to-bath-international-webinar-series/">find out about undergraduate study at Bath</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex-row flex-column-reverse-sm">
      <!-- Pinned items -->
      <div class="half-block bg-white">
        
          
            <!-- Single pinned item with image -->
            <a class="dual-block link-white bg-granite" href="/forms/order-the-2023-undergraduate-prospectus">
              <div class="flex-wrapper">
                <article class="dual-block-text">
                  <div class="link-wrapper">
                    <h3 class="link-heading">Order the 2023 undergraduate prospectus</h3>
                    <p class="link-summary">Learn about our undergraduate courses starting in September 2023, hear from our current students, and get a taste of what it's like to live in Bath.  </p>
                  </div>
                </article>
                <figure class="dual-block-image">
                  <img class="stretch" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/52153402809_5013aa45ce_o_d.jpg" alt="Students walking along the Parade on campus" loading="lazy">
                </figure>
              </div>
            </a>
          
            <!-- Single pinned item with image -->
            <a class="dual-block link-white bg-granite" href="/forms/download-the-2023-masters-prospectus">
              <div class="flex-wrapper">
                <article class="dual-block-text">
                  <div class="link-wrapper">
                    <h3 class="link-heading">Download the 2023 master's prospectus</h3>
                    <p class="link-summary">Request a download of our master's prospectus and learn about our courses starting in September 2023.</p>
                  </div>
                </article>
                <figure class="dual-block-image">
                  <img class="stretch" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/52153161721_23f407b003_o_d.jpg" alt="Students relaxing by the lake on campus" loading="lazy">
                </figure>
              </div>
            </a>
          
        
        <!-- / Pinned items -->
      </div>
      <!-- Text bucket -->
      <div class="half-block">
        <div class="text-block flex-column flex-center">
          <h1>Our rankings</h1>

<p>We're a university that's well placed to help you succeed, wherever you're from. We're <a href="/corporate-information/rankings-and-reputation/">ranked highly</a> for overall performance, student satisfaction, and graduate employment.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
