</section>

      
        <section class="tab-section bg-white" id="tab-pane-1"
  aria-hidden="false" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tab-1">
  <header>
    <h2 class="section-heading half-block screen-reader">Making an impact</h2>
  </header>
  <div class="section-wrapper">
    <div class="flex-row-reverse flex-column-sm">
      <!-- Image -->
      <div class="half-block hide-for-small-only">
        <img class="stretch" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/52153168963_f0ed3001e2_o_d.jpg" alt="Masked researcher in a lab" loading="lazy">
      </div>
      <!-- Text bucket -->
      <div class="half-block">
        <div class="text-block flex-column flex-center">
          <h1>Shaping and informing the direction of research</h1>

<p>Bath's world-leading research is improving lives and changing the world. Our enterprise and innovation deliver scientific and economic impact - benefiting communities locally, nationally, and internationally. We engage with the public, policy-makers, charities, and businesses to inform new research directions.</p>

<p>Our Doctoral College supports doctoral researchers and helps develop our <a href="/corporate-information/research-strategy">research strategy</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex-row flex-column-reverse-sm">
      <!-- Pinned items -->
      <div class="half-block bg-white">
        
          
            <!-- Single pinned item with image -->
            <a class="dual-block link-white bg-granite" href="https://www.csct.ac.uk/">
              <div class="flex-wrapper">
                <article class="dual-block-text">
                  <div class="link-wrapper">
                    <h3 class="link-heading">Centre for Sustainable and Circular Technologies (CSCT)</h3>
                    <p class="link-summary">Placing fundamental concepts of sustainability and circularity at the core of research, innovation, training and outreach in applied science and engineering. </p>
                  </div>
                </article>
                <figure class="dual-block-image">
                  <img class="stretch" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/52152154087_9a7f36a347_o_d.jpg" alt="Research student working at a piece of precision equipment" loading="lazy">
                </figure>
              </div>
            </a>
          
            <!-- Single pinned item with image -->
            <a class="dual-block link-white bg-granite" href="https://iaaps.co.uk/">
              <div class="flex-wrapper">
                <article class="dual-block-text">
                  <div class="link-wrapper">
                    <h3 class="link-heading">Institute for Advanced Automotive Propulsion Systems (IAAPS)</h3>
                    <p class="link-summary">The IAAPS team has supported propulsion research for over 40 years and offers a unique combination of academic and industrial expertise in all propulsion types.</p>
                  </div>
                </article>
                <figure class="dual-block-image">
                  <img class="stretch" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/52152154112_02ec5d565a_o_d.jpg" alt="Two IAAPS researchers look at results of an experiment on a laptop" loading="lazy">
                </figure>
              </div>
            </a>
          
        
        <!-- / Pinned items -->
      </div>
      <!-- Text bucket -->
      <div class="half-block">
        <div class="text-block flex-column flex-center">
          <h1>Tackling issues of global significance</h1>

<p>Our flexibility enables us to create agile inter-disciplinary and multi-disciplinary teams, working with pre-eminent partners worldwide, to tackle issues of global significance. </p>

<p><a href="/topics/research/">Find out more about our research</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- / Single tab -->
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

      
        <section class="tab-section bg-white" id="tab-pane-2"
  aria-hidden="false" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tab-2">
  <header>
    <h2 class="section-heading half-block screen-reader">Supporting the community</h2>
  </header>
  <div class="section-wrapper">
    <div class="flex-row-reverse flex-column-sm">
      <!-- Image -->
      <div class="half-block hide-for-small-only">
        <img class="stretch" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/52152154062_a892fa53c4_o_d.jpg" alt="Woman listens intently at a community event" loading="lazy">
      </div>
      <!-- Text bucket -->
      <div class="half-block">
        <div class="text-block flex-column flex-center">
          <h1>Working with the community</h1>

<p>Our staff and students are involved with the community in and around Bath, including partnerships with community groups and collaborations with local organisations.</p>

<p>We support local students to prepare for their future, working with their schools and colleges to inspire them to pursue further study and careers.</p>

<p>Find out more about <a href="/topics/our-place-in-the-community/">Our place in the community</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex-row flex-column-reverse-sm">
      <!-- Pinned items -->
      <div class="half-block bg-white">
        
          
            <!-- Single pinned item with image -->
            <a class="dual-block link-white bg-granite" href="https://www.bath.ac.uk/events/?f.Audience%7CZ=Public&f.Type%7CY=Lectures+and+seminars&f.Type%7CY=Conferences&f.Type%7CY=Courses+and+workshops&f.Type%7CY=Local+interest&f.Type%7CY=Open+days+and+tours&f.Type%7CY=Culture">
              <div class="flex-wrapper">
                <article class="dual-block-text">
                  <div class="link-wrapper">
                    <h3 class="link-heading">Public events</h3>
                    <p class="link-summary">Find out what's on. Join us for upcoming events, including conferences, public lectures, arts performances and exhibitions and sporting fixtures.</p>
                  </div>
                </article>
                <figure class="dual-block-image">
                  <img class="stretch" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/52153168938_9131dffbe0_o_d.jpg" alt="A woman speaks at an event" loading="lazy">
                </figure>
              </div>
            </a>
          
            <!-- Single pinned item with image -->
            <a class="dual-block link-white bg-granite" href="/topics/coronavirus-covid-19">
              <div class="flex-wrapper">
                <article class="dual-block-text">
                  <div class="link-wrapper">
                    <h3 class="link-heading">Coronavirus (COVID-19)</h3>
                    <p class="link-summary">Information, advice and guidance about coronavirus for our University community.</p>
                  </div>
                </article>
                <figure class="dual-block-image">
                  <img class="stretch" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/50320120177_336d15e2d0_o_d.jpg" alt="Be safe on campus" loading="lazy">
                </figure>
              </div>
            </a>
          
        
        <!-- / Pinned items -->
      </div>
      <!-- Text bucket -->
      <div class="half-block">
        <div class="text-block flex-column flex-center">
          <h1>Reducing our environmental impact</h1>

<p>We're reducing our environmental impact through ethical food sourcing, waste management, generating our own sustainable energy, and raising awareness of how staff and students can help. We work with the local community, industry, public sector bodies and third sector organisations, to support the transition to the net zero carbon economy.</p>

<p><a href="/topics/climate-change-and-the-university-of-bath/">Find out more about how we're reducing our carbon footprint</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- / Single tab -->
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

      
        <section class="tab-section bg-white" id="tab-pane-3"
  aria-hidden="false" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tab-3">
  <header>
    <h2 class="section-heading half-block screen-reader">Work at Bath</h2>
  </header>
  <div class="section-wrapper">
    <div class="flex-row-reverse flex-column-sm">
      <!-- Image -->
      <div class="half-block hide-for-small-only">
        <img class="stretch" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/52153659840_c0181ec179_o_d.jpg" alt="A woman smiles as she talks to two people with their backs to us" loading="lazy">
      </div>
      <!-- Text bucket -->
      <div class="half-block">
        <div class="text-block flex-column flex-center">
          <h1>Be part of a vibrant and innovative community</h1>

